Package io.papermc.paper.registry.data

Interface JukeboxSongRegistryEntry.Builder

All Superinterfaces:
JukeboxSongRegistryEntry, RegistryBuilder<JukeboxSong>
Enclosing interface:
JukeboxSongRegistryEntry
@Experimental @NonExtendable public static interface JukeboxSongRegistryEntry.Builder extends JukeboxSongRegistryEntry, RegistryBuilder<JukeboxSong>
A mutable builder for the JukeboxSongRegistryEntry plugins may change in applicable registry events.

The following values are required for each builder:

  • soundEvent(TypedKey), soundEvent(Consumer) or soundEvent(RegistryHolder)
  • description(Component)
  • lengthInSeconds(float)
  • comparatorOutput(int)
